1431
01:56:39.210 --> 01:56:40.370
Ambil surat izin dulu!

1432
01:56:40.610 --> 01:56:44.050
Nah, sementara Virat
masih mengamati dulu,


1433
01:56:44.290 --> 01:56:49.490
