1443
01:57:23.370 --> 01:57:24.650
Bagaimana caranya?

1444
01:57:24.930 --> 01:57:27.810
Kita bisa gambar guru di sini.

1445
01:57:28.130 --> 01:57:30.690
Maksudnya, guru benaran.
- Atau digunting.


1446
01:57:30.970 --> 01:57:33.770
Gurunya tumbang, karena terlalu ribut.

1447
